734 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Newobj, nullableConstructor);
735 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Stloc, local3);
736 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Br_S, label2);
737 _ilg.MarkLabel(label);
738 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldloca, local3);
739 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Initobj, resultType);
740 _ilg.MarkLabel(label2);
741 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldloc, local3);
742 FreeLocal(local3);
743 }

836 private void EmitLabelExpression(Expression expr, CompilationFlags flags)
837 {
838 LabelExpression labelExpression = (LabelExpression)expr;
839 LabelInfo info = null;
840 if (_labelBlock.Kind == LabelScopeKind.Block)
841 {
842 _labelBlock.TryGetLabelInfo(labelExpression.Target, out info);
843 if (info == null && _labelBlock.Parent.Kind == LabelScopeKind.Switch)
844 {
845 _labelBlock.Parent.TryGetLabelInfo(labelExpression.Target, out info);
846 }
847 }
848 if (info == null)
849 {
850 info = DefineLabel(labelExpression.Target);
851 }
852 if (labelExpression.DefaultValue != null)
853 {
854 if (labelExpression.Target.Type == typeof(void))
855 {
856 EmitExpressionAsVoid(labelExpression.DefaultValue, flags);
857 }
858 else
859 {
860 flags = UpdateEmitExpressionStartFlag(flags, CompilationFlags.EmitExpressionStart);
861 EmitExpression(labelExpression.DefaultValue, flags);
862 }
863 }
864 info.Mark();
865 }
866
867 private void EmitGotoExpression(Expression expr, CompilationFlags flags)
868 {
869 GotoExpression gotoExpression = (GotoExpression)expr;
870 LabelInfo labelInfo = ReferenceLabel(gotoExpression.Target);
871 CompilationFlags compilationFlags = flags & CompilationFlags.EmitAsTailCallMask;
872 if (compilationFlags != CompilationFlags.EmitAsNoTail)
873 {
874 compilationFlags = (labelInfo.CanReturn ? CompilationFlags.EmitAsTail : CompilationFlags.EmitAsNoTail);
875 flags = UpdateEmitAsTailCallFlag(flags, compilationFlags);
876 }
877 if (gotoExpression.Value != null)
878 {
879 if (gotoExpression.Target.Type == typeof(void))
880 {
881 EmitExpressionAsVoid(gotoExpression.Value, flags);
882 }
883 else
884 {
885 flags = UpdateEmitExpressionStartFlag(flags, CompilationFlags.EmitExpressionStart);
886 EmitExpression(gotoExpression.Value, flags);
887 }
888 }
889 labelInfo.EmitJump();
890 EmitUnreachable(gotoExpression, flags);
891 }

896 {
897 _ilg.EmitDefault(node.Type, this);
898 }

901 private bool TryPushLabelBlock(Expression node)
902 {
903 switch (node.NodeType)
904 {
905 default:
906 if (_labelBlock.Kind != LabelScopeKind.Expression)
907 {
908 PushLabelBlock(LabelScopeKind.Expression);
909 return true;
910 }
911 return false;
912 case ExpressionType.Label:
913 if (_labelBlock.Kind == LabelScopeKind.Block)
914 {
915 LabelTarget target = ((LabelExpression)node).Target;
916 if (_labelBlock.ContainsTarget(target))
917 {
918 return false;
919 }
920 if (_labelBlock.Parent.Kind == LabelScopeKind.Switch && _labelBlock.Parent.ContainsTarget(target))
921 {
922 return false;
923 }
924 }
925 PushLabelBlock(LabelScopeKind.Statement);
926 return true;
927 case ExpressionType.Block:
928 if (!(node is SpilledExpressionBlock))
929 {
930 PushLabelBlock(LabelScopeKind.Block);
931 if (_labelBlock.Parent.Kind != LabelScopeKind.Switch)
932 {
933 DefineBlockLabels(node);
934 }
935 return true;
936 }
937 goto default;
938 case ExpressionType.Switch:
939 {
940 PushLabelBlock(LabelScopeKind.Switch);
941 SwitchExpression switchExpression = (SwitchExpression)node;
942 foreach (SwitchCase @case in switchExpression.Cases)
943 {
944 DefineBlockLabels(@case.Body);
945 }
946 DefineBlockLabels(switchExpression.DefaultBody);
947 return true;
948 }
949 case ExpressionType.Convert:
950 if (!(node.Type != typeof(void)))
951 {
952 PushLabelBlock(LabelScopeKind.Statement);
953 return true;
954 }
955 goto default;
956 case ExpressionType.Conditional:
957 case ExpressionType.Goto:
958 case ExpressionType.Loop:
959 PushLabelBlock(LabelScopeKind.Statement);
960 return true;
961 }
962 }
963
964 private void DefineBlockLabels(Expression node)
965 {
966 if (!(node is BlockExpression blockExpression) || blockExpression is SpilledExpressionBlock)
967 {
968 return;
969 }
970 int i = 0;
971 for (int expressionCount = blockExpression.ExpressionCount; i < expressionCount; i++)
972 {
973 Expression expression = blockExpression.GetExpression(i);
974 if (expression is LabelExpression labelExpression)
975 {
976 DefineLabel(labelExpression.Target);
977 }
978 }
979 }
980
981 private void AddReturnLabel(LambdaExpression lambda)
982 {
983 Expression expression = lambda.Body;
984 while (true)
985 {
986 switch (expression.NodeType)
987 {
988 default:
989 return;
990 case ExpressionType.Label:
991 {
992 LabelTarget target = ((LabelExpression)expression).Target;
993 _labelInfo.Add(target, new LabelInfo(_ilg, target, TypeUtils.AreReferenceAssignable(lambda.ReturnType, target.Type)));
994 return;
995 }
996 case ExpressionType.Block:
997 {
998 BlockExpression blockExpression = (BlockExpression)expression;
999 if (blockExpression.ExpressionCount == 0)
1000 {
1001 return;
1002 }
1003 for (int num = blockExpression.ExpressionCount - 1; num >= 0; num--)
1004 {
1005 expression = blockExpression.GetExpression(num);
1006 if (Significant(expression))
1007 {
1008 break;
1009 }
1010 }
1011 break;
1012 }
1013 }
1014 }
1015 }

1123 {
1124 EmitExpressionAsVoid(node, CompilationFlags.EmitAsNoTail);
1125 }
1126
1127 private void EmitExpressionAsVoid(Expression node, CompilationFlags flags)
1128 {
1129 CompilationFlags flags2 = EmitExpressionStart(node);
1130 switch (node.NodeType)
1131 {
1132 case ExpressionType.Assign:
1133 EmitAssign((AssignBinaryExpression)node, CompilationFlags.EmitAsVoidType);
1134 break;
1135 case ExpressionType.Block:
1136 Emit((BlockExpression)node, UpdateEmitAsTypeFlag(flags, CompilationFlags.EmitAsVoidType));
1137 break;
1138 case ExpressionType.Throw:
1139 EmitThrow((UnaryExpression)node, CompilationFlags.EmitAsVoidType);
1140 break;
1141 case ExpressionType.Goto:
1142 EmitGotoExpression(node, UpdateEmitAsTypeFlag(flags, CompilationFlags.EmitAsVoidType));
1143 break;
1144 default:
1145 if (node.Type == typeof(void))
1146 {
1147 EmitExpression(node, UpdateEmitExpressionStartFlag(flags, CompilationFlags.EmitNoExpressionStart));
1148 break;
1149 }
1150 EmitExpression(node, CompilationFlags.EmitNoExpressionStart | CompilationFlags.EmitAsNoTail);
1151 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Pop);
1152 break;
1153 case ExpressionType.Constant:
1154 case ExpressionType.Parameter:
1155 case ExpressionType.Default:
1156 break;
1157 }
1158 EmitExpressionEnd(flags2);
1159 }

1162 {

1164 {

1167 else if (!TypeUtils.AreEquivalent(node.Type, type))
1168 {
1169 EmitExpression(node);
1170 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Castclass, type);
1171 }
1172 else
1173 {
1174 EmitExpression(node, UpdateEmitExpressionStartFlag(flags, CompilationFlags.EmitExpressionStart));
1175 }

1195 private void EmitInvocationExpression(Expression expr, CompilationFlags flags)
1196 {
1197 InvocationExpression invocationExpression = (InvocationExpression)expr;
1198 if (invocationExpression.LambdaOperand != null)
1199 {

1201 return;
1202 }

1204 if (typeof(LambdaExpression).IsAssignableFrom(expr.Type))
1205 {
1206 expr = Expression.Call(expr, LambdaExpression.GetCompileMethod(expr.Type));
1207 }
1208 EmitMethodCall(expr, expr.Type.GetInvokeMethod(), invocationExpression, CompilationFlags.EmitExpressionStart | CompilationFlags.EmitAsNoTail);

1211 private void EmitInlinedInvoke(InvocationExpression invoke, CompilationFlags flags)
1212 {

1215 LambdaCompiler lambdaCompiler = new LambdaCompiler(this, lambdaOperand, invoke);
1216 if (list != null)

1218 flags = UpdateEmitAsTailCallFlag(flags, CompilationFlags.EmitAsNoTail);

1220 lambdaCompiler.EmitLambdaBody(_scope, inlined: true, flags);

1359 private void EmitMethodCall(MethodInfo mi, IArgumentProvider args, Type objectType, CompilationFlags flags)
1360 {
1361 List<WriteBack> writeBacks = EmitArguments(mi, args);
1362 OpCode opCode = (UseVirtual(mi) ? OpCodes.Callvirt : OpCodes.Call);
1363 if (opCode == OpCodes.Callvirt && objectType.IsValueType)
1364 {
1365 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Constrained, objectType);
1366 }
1367 if ((flags & CompilationFlags.EmitAsTailCallMask) == CompilationFlags.EmitAsTail && !MethodHasByRefParameter(mi))
1368 {
1369 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Tailcall);
1370 }
1371 if (mi.CallingConvention == CallingConventions.VarArgs)
1372 {
1373 int argumentCount = args.ArgumentCount;
1374 Type[] array = new Type[argumentCount];
1375 for (int i = 0; i < argumentCount; i++)
1376 {
1377 array[i] = args.GetArgument(i).Type;
1378 }
1379 _ilg.EmitCall(opCode, mi, array);
1380 }
1381 else
1382 {
1383 _ilg.Emit(opCode, mi);
1384 }
1385 EmitWriteBack(writeBacks);
1386 }

1389 {
1390 ParameterInfo[] parametersCached = mi.GetParametersCached();
1391 foreach (ParameterInfo pi in parametersCached)
1392 {
1393 if (pi.IsByRefParameter())
1394 {
1395 return true;
1396 }
1397 }
1398 return false;
1399 }

1401 private void EmitCall(Type objectType, MethodInfo method)
1402 {
1403 if (method.CallingConvention == CallingConventions.VarArgs)
1404 {
1405 throw Error.UnexpectedVarArgsCall(method);
1406 }
1407 OpCode opCode = (UseVirtual(method) ? OpCodes.Callvirt : OpCodes.Call);
1408 if (opCode == OpCodes.Callvirt && objectType.IsValueType)
1409 {
1410 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Constrained, objectType);
1411 }
1412 _ilg.Emit(opCode, method);
1413 }

1416 {
1417 if (mi.IsStatic)
1418 {
1419 return false;
1420 }
1421 if (mi.DeclaringType.IsValueType)
1422 {
1423 return false;
1424 }
1425 return true;

1433 private List<WriteBack> EmitArguments(MethodBase method, IArgumentProvider args, int skipParameters)
1434 {
1435 ParameterInfo[] parametersCached = method.GetParametersCached();
1436 List<WriteBack> list = null;
1437 int i = skipParameters;
1438 for (int num = parametersCached.Length; i < num; i++)
1439 {
1440 ParameterInfo parameterInfo = parametersCached[i];
1441 Expression argument = args.GetArgument(i - skipParameters);
1442 Type parameterType = parameterInfo.ParameterType;
1443 if (parameterType.IsByRef)
1444 {
1445 parameterType = parameterType.GetElementType();
1446 WriteBack writeBack = EmitAddressWriteBack(argument, parameterType);
1447 if (writeBack != null)
1448 {
1449 if (list == null)
1450 {
1451 list = new List<WriteBack>();
1452 }
1453 list.Add(writeBack);
1454 }
1455 }
1456 else
1457 {
1458 EmitExpression(argument);
1459 }
1460 }
1461 return list;
1462 }

1468 return;

1471 {
1472 writeBack(this);
1473 }
1474 }

1476 private void EmitConstantExpression(Expression expr)
1477 {

1495 private void EmitDynamicExpression(Expression expr)
1496 {
1497 IDynamicExpression dynamicExpression = (IDynamicExpression)expr;
1498 object obj = dynamicExpression.CreateCallSite();
1499 Type type = obj.GetType();
1500 MethodInfo invokeMethod = dynamicExpression.DelegateType.GetInvokeMethod();
1501 EmitConstant(obj, type);
1502 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Dup);
1503 LocalBuilder local = GetLocal(type);
1504 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Stloc, local);
1505 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldfld, GetCallSiteTargetField(type));
1506 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldloc, local);
1507 FreeLocal(local);
1508 List<WriteBack> writeBacks = EmitArguments(invokeMethod, dynamicExpression, 1);
1509 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Callvirt, invokeMethod);
1510 EmitWriteBack(writeBacks);
1511 }

1541 private void EmitTypeBinaryExpression(Expression expr)
1542 {
1543 TypeBinaryExpression typeBinaryExpression = (TypeBinaryExpression)expr;
1544 if (typeBinaryExpression.NodeType == ExpressionType.TypeEqual)
1545 {
1546 EmitExpression(typeBinaryExpression.ReduceTypeEqual());
1547 return;
1548 }
1549 Type type = typeBinaryExpression.Expression.Type;
1550 AnalyzeTypeIsResult analyzeTypeIsResult = ConstantCheck.AnalyzeTypeIs(typeBinaryExpression);
1551 switch (analyzeTypeIsResult)
1552 {
1553 case AnalyzeTypeIsResult.KnownFalse:
1554 case AnalyzeTypeIsResult.KnownTrue:
1555 EmitExpressionAsVoid(typeBinaryExpression.Expression);
1556 _ilg.EmitPrimitive(analyzeTypeIsResult == AnalyzeTypeIsResult.KnownTrue);
1557 return;
1558 case AnalyzeTypeIsResult.KnownAssignable:
1559 if (type.IsNullableType())
1560 {
1561 EmitAddress(typeBinaryExpression.Expression, type);
1562 _ilg.EmitHasValue(type);
1563 }
1564 else
1565 {
1566 EmitExpression(typeBinaryExpression.Expression);
1567 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldnull);
1568 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Cgt_Un);
1569 }
1570 return;
1571 }
1572 EmitExpression(typeBinaryExpression.Expression);
1573 if (type.IsValueType)
1574 {
1575 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Box, type);
1576 }
1577 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Isinst, typeBinaryExpression.TypeOperand);
1578 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldnull);
1579 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Cgt_Un);
1580 }

2109 CompilationFlags flags2 = (flag ? EmitExpressionStart(node) : CompilationFlags.EmitNoExpressionStart);

3551 ConstructorInfo nullableConstructor = TypeUtils.GetNullableConstructor(resultType);
3552 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Newobj, nullableConstructor);
3553 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Br_S, label2);
3554 _ilg.MarkLabel(label);
3555 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldloc, local);
3556 FreeLocal(local);
3557 _ilg.MarkLabel(label2);
3558 return;
3559 }
3560 switch (op)
3561 {
3562 case ExpressionType.Not:
3563 if (operandType == typeof(bool))
3564 {
3565 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldc_I4_0);
3566 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ceq);
3567 return;
3568 }
3569 goto case ExpressionType.OnesComplement;
3570 case ExpressionType.OnesComplement:
3571 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Not);
3572 if (!operandType.IsUnsigned())
3573 {
3574 return;
3575 }
3576 break;
3577 case ExpressionType.IsFalse:
3578 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldc_I4_0);
3579 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ceq);
3580 return;
3581 case ExpressionType.IsTrue:
3582 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldc_I4_1);
3583 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ceq);
3584 return;
3585 case ExpressionType.UnaryPlus:
3586 return;
3587 case ExpressionType.Negate:
3588 case ExpressionType.NegateChecked:
3589 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Neg);
3590 return;
3591 case ExpressionType.TypeAs:
3592 if (operandType != resultType)
3593 {
3594 if (operandType.IsValueType)
3595 {
3596 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Box, operandType);
3597 }
3598 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Isinst, resultType);
3599 if (resultType.IsNullableType())
3600 {
3601 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Unbox_Any, resultType);
3602 }
3603 }
3604 return;
3605 case ExpressionType.Increment:
3606 EmitConstantOne(resultType);
3607 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Add);
3608 break;
3609 case ExpressionType.Decrement:
3610 EmitConstantOne(resultType);
3611 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Sub);
3612 break;
3613 }
3614 EmitConvertArithmeticResult(op, resultType);
3615 }

3617 private void EmitConstantOne(Type type)
3618 {
3619 switch (type.GetTypeCode())
3620 {
3621 case TypeCode.Int64:
3622 case TypeCode.UInt64:
3623 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldc_I4_1);
3624 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Conv_I8);
3625 break;
3626 case TypeCode.Single:
3627 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldc_R4, 1f);
3628 break;
3629 case TypeCode.Double:
3630 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldc_R8, 1.0);
3631 break;
3632 default:
3633 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Ldc_I4_1);
3634 break;
3635 }
3636 }

3641 EmitExpression(unaryExpression.Operand);
3642 _ilg.Emit(OpCodes.Unbox_Any, unaryExpression.Type);

3650 private void EmitConvert(UnaryExpression node, CompilationFlags flags)
3651 {
3652 if (node.Method != null)
3653 {
3654 if (!node.IsLifted || (node.Type.IsValueType && node.Operand.Type.IsValueType))
3655 {
3656 EmitUnaryMethod(node, flags);
3657 return;
3658 }
3659 ParameterInfo[] parametersCached = node.Method.GetParametersCached();
3660 Type type = parametersCached[0].ParameterType;
3661 if (type.IsByRef)
3662 {
3663 type = type.GetElementType();
3664 }
3665 UnaryExpression arg = Expression.Convert(node.Operand, type);
3666 node = Expression.Convert(Expression.Call(node.Method, arg), node.Type);
3667 }
3668 if (node.Type == typeof(void))
3669 {
3670 EmitExpressionAsVoid(node.Operand, flags);
3671 return;
3672 }
3673 if (TypeUtils.AreEquivalent(node.Operand.Type, node.Type))
3674 {
3675 EmitExpression(node.Operand, flags);
3676 return;
3677 }
3678 EmitExpression(node.Operand);
3679 _ilg.EmitConvertToType(node.Operand.Type, node.Type, node.NodeType == ExpressionType.ConvertChecked, this);
3680 }
3681
3682 private void EmitUnaryMethod(UnaryExpression node, CompilationFlags flags)
3683 {
3684 if (node.IsLifted)
3685 {
3686 ParameterExpression parameterExpression = Expression.Variable(node.Operand.Type.GetNonNullableType(), null);
3687 MethodCallExpression methodCallExpression = Expression.Call(node.Method, parameterExpression);
3688 Type nullableType = methodCallExpression.Type.GetNullableType();
3689 EmitLift(node.NodeType, nullableType, methodCallExpression, new ParameterExpression[1] { parameterExpression }, new Expression[1] { node.Operand });
3690 _ilg.EmitConvertToType(nullableType, node.Type, isChecked: false, this);
3691 }
3692 else
3693 {
3694 EmitMethodCallExpression(Expression.Call(node.Method, node.Operand), flags);
3695 }
3696 }
